.SH Name
.SP 5 5
strip_colours -  This method strips the colour codes out of the resultant string.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string strip_colours(string str)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^str%^RESET%^ - the string to strip
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
