.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/secure/simul_efun/strip_colours.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method strips the colour codes out of the resultant string.
This is used to send strings to systems outside the mud (like
the web and stuff).
.EP

